data.description: ***MOTIVATED SELLERS!!!*** The sellers are offering an incredible $10,000 buyer credit. Use it to buy down your interest rate, reducing your monthly mortgage payments, or apply it towards closing costs with an acceptable offer. This is a fantastic opportunity to save and make this home even more affordable. Welcome to this charming home in Converse! This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem offers a generous 2,149 square feet of living space nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac. Step inside and be captivated by the expansive open floor plan, perfect for entertaining and creating lasting memories.  The main level boasts a convenient primary bedroom, providing a private retreat for relaxation. Upstairs, you'll find generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for family and guests. With plenty of room to grow, this home offers the flexibility to meet your needs.    Outside, discover a huge backyard, ready to be transformed into your personal oasis. Whether you envision a lush garden, a play area for children, or a tranquil retreat, the possibilities are endless. Don't wait another moment to make this home yours. Schedule your showing today and take the first step towards a lifetime of memories in this Converse gem.  Lease back desired. Any mounted TV's and curtains with rods do NOT convey.
